OL,4,Cpayers almost #200,000
OL,6,FA tiny typo has cost Bristol council
OL,7,Ftax payers almost #200,000 as a result
OL,8,Fof an error on council tax bills.
OL,10,FLast month Bristol City Council sent
OL,11,Fout 239,143 letters explaining a
OL,12,F"typographical error" on this year's
OL,13,Fcouncil tax bill. By law the council
OL,14,Fhad to write to households explaining
OL,15,Ftheir mistake.
