OL,3,CTiny typo costs Bristol council tax
OL,4,Cpayers almost #200,000
OL,6,FThe original error was based on
OL,7,Finformation which breaks down details
OL,8,Fof the annual council tax bill. As
OL,9,Fpart of the overall bill a small
OL,10,Fprecept goes towards the Avon Fire
OL,11,FAuthority and the Police and Crime
OL,12,FCommissioner for Avon and Somerset.
OL,13,FThis year these precepts increased by
OL,14,Ffive per cent for the commissioner and
OL,15,F5.9 per cent for the fire authority.
