OL,3,CTiny typo costs Bristol council tax
OL,4,Cpayers almost #200,000
OL,6,FA council spokesperson said: "All
OL,7,Fhouseholds who had received a council
OL,8,Ftax bill during the current financial
OL,9,Fyear received the letter of
OL,10,Fclarification. The cost of print and
OL,11,Fpostage for the letters was #198k.
OL,13,F"The current process has been
OL,14,Freviewed, and we have introduced
OL,15,Fadditional steps to its sign off. This
OL,16,Fwill mean after IT and accounting have
OL,17,Fsigned off the figures they will then
OL,18,Fbe checked a further time by the
OL,19,Fcouncil tax manager."
