OL,6,F"While the council tax bill you
OL,7,Freceived was, and remains, correct,
OL,8,Fthe percentage increase shown for both
OL,9,FAvon Fire Authority and the PCC for
OL,10,FAvon and Somerset were transposed."
OL,12,F"Please accept my apologies for any
OL,13,Finconvenience caused."
